org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.common.profile.Codegen

Interface CodegenPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    CodegenPackage

    public static interface CodegenPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each operation of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
